raw_body: KULANDRA (KULEN) RATNESER – 18.03.1933-21.08.2023 – Passed away peacefully in Darwin on 21st August,​ 2023 aged 90. Beloved husband of Sujatha. Dearly loved father of Rajiv and Sanjiv and father-in-law of Jane and Monique,​ much loved grandfather of Grace,​ William,​ Teddy,​ Milo and Lucky,​ steadfast guardian of our laws till the end. Loved and remembered always. Rest in peace. The Memorial Service for Kulandra Ratneser of Nedlands will be held at Christ Church School Chapel,​ Queenslea Drive,​ Claremont in Western Australia at 11.00 a.m. (GMT+8) on Saturday 09.09.2023. To view the livestream,​ please visit our website – www.bowraodea.com.au056014
